description:
A brief but comprehensive overview of what science knows and does not know about climate change at the start of 2009.

Very interesting live presentation given by a leading climate scientist at the 25C3 Chaos Communication Conference in Berlin 2008-12-30.



Language spoken: English

Duration: 64 minutes

Resolution: 720x576



